forward ports, please use the rich language\&.
.RE
.PP
[\fB\-\-zone\fR=\fIzone\fR] [\fB\-\-policy\fR=\fIpolicy\fR] \fB\-\-query\-forward\-port\fR=port=\fIportid\fR[\-\fIportid\fR]:proto=\fIprotocol\fR[:toport=\fIportid\fR[\-\fIportid\fR]][:toaddr=\fIaddress\fR[/\fImask\fR]]
