Return whether the
\fIIPv4\fR
forward port has been added\&. Returns 0 if true, 1 otherwise\&.
.sp
For
\fIIPv6\fR
forward ports, please use the rich language\&.
.RE
.PP
[\fB\-\-zone\fR=\fIzone\fR] [\fB\-\-policy\fR=\fIpolicy\fR] \fB\-\-list\-source\-ports\fR
