.PP
[\fB\-\-zone\fR=\fIzone\fR] [\fB\-\-policy\fR=\fIpolicy\fR] \fB\-\-remove\-masquerade\fR
.RS 4
Disable
\fIIPv4\fR
masquerade\&.
.sp
For
\fIIPv6\fR
masquerading, please use the rich language\&.
.RE
.PP
[\fB\-\-zone\fR=\fIzone\fR] [\fB\-\-policy\fR=\fIpolicy\fR] \fB\-\-query\-masquerade\fR
.RS 4
Return whether
\fIIPv4\fR
masquerading has been enabled\&. Returns 0 if true, 1 otherwise\&.
.sp
For
\fIIPv6\fR
masquerading, please use the rich language\&.
.RE
.PP
[\fB\-\-zone\fR=\fIzone\fR] [\fB\-\-policy\fR=\fIpolicy\fR] \fB\-\-list\-rich\-rules\fR
.RS 4
List rich language rules added as a newline separated list\&.
.RE
