[\fB\-\-zone\fR=\fIzone\fR] [\fB\-\-policy\fR=\fIpolicy\fR] \fB\-\-add\-rich\-rule\fR=\*(Aq\fIrule\fR\*(Aq
.RS 4
Add rich language rule \*(Aq\fIrule\fR\*(Aq\&. This option can be specified multiple times\&.
