For the rich language rule syntax, please have a look at
\fBfirewalld.richlanguage\fR(5)\&.
.RE
.PP
[\fB\-\-zone\fR=\fIzone\fR] [\fB\-\-policy\fR=\fIpolicy\fR] \fB\-\-remove\-rich\-rule\fR=\*(Aq\fIrule\fR\*(Aq
