\fB\-\-ipset\fR=\fIipset\fR \fB\-\-remove\-entry\fR=\fIentry\fR
.RS 4
Remove an entry from the ipset\&.
.RE
.PP
\fB\-\-ipset\fR=\fIipset\fR \fB\-\-query\-entry\fR=\fIentry\fR
